      <p>For investigating the accuracy of predicting siRNA efficacy for each characteristic method, the prediction models of each method were trained by SVR with 10-fold cross-validation using dataset A. The results of each characteristic method with SVR are shown in <xref ref-type="table" rid="pone-0027602-t002">Table 2</xref>.</p>
